steps.html_instructions: Head west on W Washington St toward N 1st Ave
Turn right to merge onto I-10 E toward Tucson
Take exit 147A-147B for AZ-202 Loop E/AZ-51 N
Keep right at the fork to continue on Exit 147A, follow signs for AZ-202 Loop E
Keep left to continue toward AZ-202 Loop E

Turn left onto AZ-87 N/N Country Club Dr
Continue to follow AZ-87 N

Turn right to merge onto I-40 E
Entering New Mexico
Take exit 159B-159C for I-25 N/I-25 S toward Santa Fe/Las Cruces

Keep left at the fork to continue on Exit 159C, follow signs for I-25 N/Santa Fe and merge onto I-25 N
Entering Colorado
Take exit Exit 15 toward US-160 E/Kit Carson Trail

Turn right onto 160 Hwy Bypass/E Goddard Ave (signs for Kit Carson Tr)
Continue to follow 160 Hwy Bypass

Turn left onto US-350 E/E Main St
Continue to follow US-350 E

Turn left onto CO-109 N/Adams Ave
Continue to follow CO-109 N

Take the 3rd left onto Co Rd 31/1st St
Continue to follow Co Rd 31
Turn right onto KS-383 N/US-36 E (signs for State Route Kansas 383)

Turn right onto US-34 E/US-6 E/4th Ave
Continue to follow US-34 E/US-6 E

Turn left onto US-6 E/W O St
Continue to follow W O St
